					<font size="12"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[1. Did you use FFPE tissue with a fixation duration of 12-24 hrs for 5mm pieces in standard buffered formalin solution for RNA isolation?
<br><font color="#004280">should</font>]]></text>
