				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The Self-Assessment Survey (SAS) and SAS report generated is intended only for the person(s) or entity to which it is addressed. The SAS report is to be treated confidentially. Any review, retransmission, dissemination, reproduction or other use of, or taking of any action in reliance upon this information by persons or entities other than the intended recipient is prohibited unless express written permission has been obtained from BBMRI-ERIC.]]></text>
